query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('differential-geometry',
'differential-topology',
'euclidean-geometry',
'fourier-analysis',
'group-theory',
'metric-spaces',
'multivariable-calculus',
'propositional-calculus',
'real-numbers',
'representation-theory',
'riemannian-geometry',
'roots',
'soft-question',
'triangles')
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
